content.body:
I agree - a userland polyfill of this is trivial with a mapper, but less so with a comparator:

```
function* distinct(iter) {
	const set = new Set();
	for (const val of iter) {
		if (!set.has(val) {
			set.add(val);
			yield val;
		}
	}
}

```

